{"tid":281334,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(JJ插沙) 我有頭皮問題....","createTime":"2017-06-12T15:33:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T17:03:58.000Z","uid":22575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"91e5cc5b5c05e3911055cf44142f3d9016e56a18","tid":281334,"uid":22575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:33:19.000Z","msg":"近呢兩個月唔知點解甩好多頭皮 , 好困擾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多位巴打絲打有沒咩醫頭皮既洗頭水 / 方法可以介紹比小弟知 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5baf57c8ab984d24942b79994fdb869fd201a6","tid":281334,"uid":120581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:35:46.000Z","msg":"普通用返啲去頭皮洗頭水咪得囉"},{"pid":"20e503a47545a8dd8f76e7e7352607c3f514e926","tid":281334,"uid":106589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:37:32.000Z","msg":"係咪染過搞過個頭啊？"},{"pid":"c93b11bd7d1c961cfd00023ec905feaa189b4b3f","tid":281334,"uid":85805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:39:02.000Z","msg":"轉洗頭水。<br />\n換到唔痕冇頭皮為止"},{"pid":"6b5294ec0222b3a930d19e8212dca507620e066a","tid":281334,"uid":53648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:50:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6bfaab69088154cd292b7bad5840ace77e68df13","tid":281334,"uid":22575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪染過搞過個頭啊？</blockquote><br />\n無染過無電過, 大概2個月都會轉一次洗頭水 <br />\n真係好苦惱完全諗唔明咩原因 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278cb81b31cacd03cc166d76f5f288c110071d84","tid":281334,"uid":22575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/gp/aw/d/B001ETUD5I/ref=yo_ii_img?ie=UTF8&amp;psc=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.uk%2Fgp%2Faw%2Fd%2FB001ETUD5I%2Fref%3Dyo_ii_img%3Fie%3DUTF8%26psc%3D1&d=0UCTjlpnd%2BMDSb3Pfcc49dibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=20350f6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.co.uk/gp/aw/d/B001ETUD5I/ref=yo_ii_img?ie=UTF8&amp;psc=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/aw/d/B00AINMFAC/ref=yo_ii_img?ie=UTF8&amp;psc=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Faw%2Fd%2FB00AINMFAC%2Fref%3Dyo_ii_img%3Fie%3DUTF8%26psc%3D1&d=0UCTjlpnd%2BMDSb3Pfcc49dibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=04d46b5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/gp/aw/d/B00AINMFAC/ref=yo_ii_img?ie=UTF8&amp;psc=1</a><br />\n<br />\n兩隻都要買 用紅色先 唔急嘅就跟佢個說明嚟用 <br />\n急嘅就最少都要隔一日先好再用多一次 大概一個禮拜就見效 <br />\n<br />\n見到用咗兩個禮拜多啲之後 就隔3-5日用一次 情況好轉咗好多就跟佢正常指示用 期間冇用紅色嗰隻可以用藍色嗰隻頂住當 <br />\n<br />\n留意返有不良反應嘅話就唔好用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻要係amazon 先有 ? 香港會唔會有得買？？"},{"pid":"6de50f98c8ca6a22bc3865d394b8443959198055","tid":281334,"uid":22575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉洗頭水。<br />\n換到唔痕冇頭皮為止</blockquote><br />\n呢兩個月大大話話換左 4 ~ 5個牌字都沒一隻得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62cdbb24044ad02150a4e49b9e45f7cd66067d8","tid":281334,"uid":53648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:54:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fa45e09538a187d61c3b6e2bd0b79a927ef2915","tid":281334,"uid":53648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47b18541be4d9875b02df554948bdf34bf18d9e9","tid":281334,"uid":38968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:55:20.000Z","msg":"我前排都係咁<br />\n轉咗洗頭水冇呢個問題<br />\n又或者你沖頭嘅水太熱都會容易有頭皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8261162e673a48901602a9591ebe847c7559247b","tid":281334,"uid":22575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:01:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我前排都係咁<br />\n轉咗洗頭水冇呢個問題<br />\n又或者你沖頭嘅水太熱都會容易有頭皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屋企用電子水爐 , 大概用 37度沖, 應該唔算太熱? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ce9a49ccb2ee4718e886e6d54bc934472383c8","tid":281334,"uid":22575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>轉洗頭水。<br />\n換到唔痕冇頭皮為止</blockquote><br />\n呢兩個月大大話話換左 4 ~ 5個牌字都沒一隻得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前同你差唔多 依家好返哂</blockquote><br />\n唔該哂巴打 , 試下去 Amazon 買黎用睇下有沒改善 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d35e86a48d192238d2c7423cdd04cc2a83a62cf","tid":281334,"uid":85805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>轉洗頭水。<br />\n換到唔痕冇頭皮為止</blockquote><br />\n呢兩個月大大話話換左 4 ~ 5個牌字都沒一隻得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n換過咩？<br />\n沙宣？<br />\n會唔會試下啲天然洗頭水？<br />\n不含矽個d"},{"pid":"a0a5903a32a3d13d5e9b0eafcb4991f9ad308f8a","tid":281334,"uid":85805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:16:45.000Z","msg":"唔建議用個啲聲稱去頭皮個啲洗頭水。<br />\n另外 未必又關洗頭水事<br />\n可能係洗頭嘅力度 唔好找到啲頭皮<br />\n用手指頭輕按頭皮<br />\n洗頭水吱上手掌度加少少水 起泡先好擺上頭<br />\n沖水唔好太熱"},{"pid":"4c8dd1c82aabd9c64263c18dd3ce5b2d7b2d4a89","tid":281334,"uid":92600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/gp/aw/d/B001ETUD5I/ref=yo_ii_img?ie=UTF8&amp;psc=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.uk%2Fgp%2Faw%2Fd%2FB001ETUD5I%2Fref%3Dyo_ii_img%3Fie%3DUTF8%26psc%3D1&d=0UCTjlpn